01:19:46,070 --> 01:19:47,940
He said...

782
01:19:52,240 --> 01:19:55,160
...he was closer to his goal...

783
01:19:57,040 --> 01:19:59,790
...than l could possibly imagine.

784
01:20:02,040 --> 01:20:03,540
Do you remember?

785
01:20:07,550 --> 01:20:12,090
See, l was led to believe...

786
01:20:14,390 --> 01:20:18,310
...he had saved my life...

787
01:20:21,060 --> 01:20:23,060
...when, in fact...

788
01:20:24,940 --> 01:20:26,570
...all the time...

789
01:20:30,070 --> 01:20:31,990
...he intended to take it.

790
01:20:35,990 --> 01:20:39,250
He intended to, um...

791
01:20:40,580 --> 01:20:42,790
What? Use me.

792
01:20:42,960 --> 01:20:49,300
He intended to use my DNA
to stop your regression.

793
01:20:54,090 --> 01:20:55,640
Well, anyway...

794
01:20:57,890 --> 01:21:00,350
...he is dead...

795
01:21:00,520 --> 01:21:03,520
...and Montgomery is...

796
01:21:03,690 --> 01:21:06,110
...heh, insane...

797
01:21:09,650 --> 01:21:11,780
...and has...

798
01:21:14,950 --> 01:21:17,370
He's destroyed all the serum.

799
01:21:38,260 --> 01:21:39,600
[LAUGHS]

800
01:21:48,570 --> 01:21:50,110
Go.

801
01:21:52,070 --> 01:21:53,740
Go!

802
01:22:18,050 --> 01:22:20,050
[ROARS]

803
01:22:25,850 --> 01:22:26,890
Aah...

804
01:22:38,870 --> 01:22:41,740
[PANTS THEN HICCUPS]

805
01:22:46,040 --> 01:22:48,080
The guns!

806
01:23:16,900 --> 01:23:18,450
[CREATURES GRUNTING]

807
01:23:28,000 --> 01:23:30,000
[ROARS]

808
01:24:00,200 --> 01:24:02,200
[AISSA GASPS]

809
01:24:44,740 --> 01:24:46,660
How do you do, sir?

810
01:24:46,830 --> 01:24:48,410
I believe we've met.

811
01:24:48,580 --> 01:24:50,660
[LAUGHS]

812
01:24:50,960 --> 01:24:54,330
Drip, drap, drip, drap.

813
01:24:54,500 --> 01:24:57,170
And where are you going
in the woods today, little girl?

814
01:24:57,550 --> 01:24:59,170
Oh, my little kitten.

815
01:24:59,340 --> 01:25:01,010
[SNICKERS]

816
01:25:01,170 --> 01:25:02,420
Fetch!

817
01:25:02,590 --> 01:25:04,010
[CREATURES GROWLING]

818
01:25:13,770 --> 01:25:15,770
[HISSES]

819
01:25:18,860 --> 01:25:20,400
[AISSA CATERWAULING]

820
01:25:28,410 --> 01:25:29,580
[DOUGLAS & AISSA GRUNTING]

821
01:25:38,040 --> 01:25:41,760
Nicely now, little kitten,
or I'll hurt you.

822
01:25:41,920 --> 01:25:43,550
[AISSA CATERWAULS]

823
01:25:47,390 --> 01:25:51,560
Remember?... Remember
how the master whipped me?

824
01:25:51,720 --> 01:25:53,390
Ooh...

825
01:25:54,480 --> 01:25:57,730
But he never touched
your soft skin, did he?

826
01:25:57,900 --> 01:25:59,570
No!

827
01:25:59,730 --> 01:26:01,730
[NECK CRACKS]

828
01:26:07,910 --> 01:26:09,530
[SNARLING]

829
01:26:13,120 --> 01:26:15,120
[ALL GIBBERING AND GRUNTING]

830
01:26:22,590 --> 01:26:24,590
[SHRIEKS]

831
01:26:33,350 --> 01:26:35,390
Come on. Come on.

832
01:26:50,280 --> 01:26:54,950
Tell them that I am the law.

833
01:26:55,120 --> 01:26:59,790
Do not believe him.
He is not the law! Unh!

834
01:27:03,460 --> 01:27:05,300
AZAZELLO:
Hyena!

835
01:27:08,970 --> 01:27:10,970
[DOUGLAS GRUNTING]

836
01:27:12,100 --> 01:27:13,510
Good doggie.

837
01:27:13,680 --> 01:27:14,970
[LAUGHS]

838
01:27:15,140 --> 01:27:16,980
[ROARING]

839
01:27:30,280 --> 01:27:31,320
[DOUGLAS YELLS]

840
01:27:31,490 --> 01:27:33,240
[HYENA LAUGHS]

841
01:27:34,790 --> 01:27:37,870
[GROWLS THEN SNARLS]

842
01:27:38,540 --> 01:27:40,790
Fine man...

843
01:27:43,000 --> 01:27:46,000
...please tell them...

844
01:27:46,170 --> 01:27:49,630
...that I am god. Hm?

845
01:27:55,010 --> 01:27:57,020
[ALL YELLING AND GROANING]

846
01:28:04,860 --> 01:28:06,860
[SHRIEKS]

847
01:28:14,490 --> 01:28:15,700
You're right.

848
01:28:18,330 --> 01:28:20,750
- You are a god.
- No!

849
01:28:24,040 --> 01:28:25,040
Again.

850
01:28:26,090 --> 01:28:29,510
You are a god.

851
01:28:30,590 --> 01:28:32,130
You're all gods.

852
01:28:35,260 --> 01:28:37,260
[HYENA CHUCKLES THEN SNARLS]

853
01:28:42,230 --> 01:28:44,020
Tell them...

854
01:28:46,440 --> 01:28:51,070
...to obey me
like they did the father.

855
01:28:54,240 --> 01:28:57,200
You all killed the father.

856
01:28:58,410 --> 01:29:01,710
You all ate his flesh.

857
01:29:03,080 --> 01:29:06,500
So who is the new father?

858
01:29:08,760 --> 01:29:13,840
Who is god number one?

859
01:29:17,930 --> 01:29:20,100
Who should they obey?

860
01:29:23,270 --> 01:29:24,560
Him?

861
01:29:24,730 --> 01:29:26,270
[GROWLS]

862
01:29:27,270 --> 01:29:28,940
Or him?

863
01:29:30,860 --> 01:29:34,280
You see, there must be...

864
01:29:34,660 --> 01:29:38,120
...a god number one.

865
01:29:39,120 --> 01:29:41,120
[GROWLING]

866
01:29:49,300 --> 01:29:50,500
[ROARS]

867
01:30:07,560 --> 01:30:09,560
[SHRIEKS]

868
01:30:33,630 --> 01:30:35,630
[CREATURES GRUNTING
AND SHRIEKING]

869
01:30:46,890 --> 01:30:48,190
[GROWLING]

870
01:30:51,860 --> 01:30:53,530
[SNARLING]

871
01:31:06,370 --> 01:31:07,910
HYENA:
Father.

872
01:31:14,170 --> 01:31:16,170
[HYENA GROANING]

873
01:31:25,480 --> 01:31:27,480
[CREATURES GRUNTING]

874
01:31:48,660 --> 01:31:50,670
[SNARLING]

875
01:32:06,470 --> 01:32:08,770
Father.

876
01:32:11,730 --> 01:32:19,950
Why?

877
01:32:31,750 --> 01:32:33,330
CREATURE:
You!

878
01:32:34,590 --> 01:32:35,880
Stay.

879
01:32:36,050 --> 01:32:39,130
Douglas, you stay here.

880
01:32:39,840 --> 01:32:42,300
You stay with us.

881
01:32:42,470 --> 01:32:46,300
I'll be back.

882
01:32:46,470 --> 01:32:48,470
[CREATURE WHIMPERING]

883
01:32:57,190 --> 01:32:59,990
I'll come back.

884
01:33:00,150 --> 01:33:02,360
There must be people
who can, uh...

885
01:33:04,620 --> 01:33:08,160
Doctors, scientists...

886
01:33:08,910 --> 01:33:11,410
...who might understand
what Moreau was trying to do.

887
01:33:11,790 --> 01:33:14,750
Perhaps they could develop a serum,
stop the regression.

888
01:33:14,920 --> 01:33:16,460
No.

889
01:33:17,630 --> 01:33:19,090
No more scientists...

890
01:33:19,960 --> 01:33:23,680
...no more laboratories,
no more experiments.

891
01:33:25,760 --> 01:33:27,970
I thought you would be able
to understand that.

892
01:33:31,180 --> 01:33:33,850
We have to be what we are...

893
01:33:35,480 --> 01:33:37,480
...not what the father
tried to make us.

894
01:33:40,570 --> 01:33:42,490
To go on two legs...

895
01:33:47,950 --> 01:33:49,620
...is very hard.

896
01:33:55,420 --> 01:33:59,920
Perhaps four is better anyway.

897
01:34:54,230 --> 01:34:57,810
DOUGLAS:
This is a true record of what l saw.

898
01:35:00,150 --> 01:35:03,780
I set it down leaving out only the latitude
and longitude of the island...

899
01:35:05,190 --> 01:35:09,240
...as a warning to all who would follow
in Moreau's footsteps.

900
01:35:12,410 --> 01:35:17,120
Most times, I keep the memory
far in the back of my mind...

901
01:35:17,290 --> 01:35:19,460
...a distant cloud.

902
01:35:21,130 --> 01:35:24,710
But there are times when
the little cloud spreads...

903
01:35:24,880 --> 01:35:27,630
...until it obscures the sky.

904
01:35:29,180 --> 01:35:31,970
At those times, I look about me
at my fellow man...

905
01:35:32,140 --> 01:35:36,520
...and l'm reminded of some likeness
to the beast people...

906
01:35:37,640 --> 01:35:41,310
...and I feel as though the animal
is surging up in them...

907
01:35:41,480 --> 01:35:44,480
...and they're neither wholly
animal nor wholly man...

908
01:35:44,650 --> 01:35:47,820
...but an unstable combination
of both...

909
01:35:48,570 --> 01:35:52,780
...as unstable as anything
Moreau created.

910
01:35:56,790 --> 01:35:59,000
And l go...

911
01:36:00,330 --> 01:36:01,710
...in fear.

912
01:40:26,020 --> 01:40:28,020
[English - US - SDH]

